This paper discusses a clustering algorithm for efficient energy utilization in wireless sensor networks, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the use of routing protocols, which could fall under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The use of clustering algorithms and optimization techniques could also fall under machine learning (cs.MA). The paper discusses the design of a protocol for heterogeneous networks, which could fall under control systems (cs.SY) or information theory (cs.IT).
